---
import svgPinkStar from '../assets/pink-star.svg'
---

<section id="about" class="py-20 px-5">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <img src={svgPinkStar.src} alt="svg" width="50" class="mb-6" />
    <h2 class="text-4xl font-medium mb-8">About Asli</h2>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-10 border-t-2 pt-8">
      <div class="space-y-4 text-base leading-relaxed">
        <p>I'm a Product Marketing Manager with experience across enterprise Linux (Canonical), B2B SaaS telecoms, and global programmatic media (PHD Media / Omnicom).</p>
        <p>I specialise in making complex technical products legible to buyers, to sales teams, to partners, and in building the GTM infrastructure that turns that clarity into measurable pipeline. I'm equally at home in B2B tech, luxury, and media contexts.</p>
        <p>Before marketing, I competed for the Turkish National Ski Team. I hold a BSc in Economics & Management from King's College London and a DALF C1 in French, and I've co-authored a peer-reviewed research paper. Based between London and Istanbul. Open to senior PMM roles across Europe.</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">English · Turkish (native) · French (DALF C1)</p>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <a href="mailto:aslialimesimsek@gmail.com" class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-medium underline underline-offset-4">
          <i class="ri-mail-line"></i> aslialimesimsek@gmail.com
        </a>
        <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/aslialimesimsek" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-medium underline underline-offset-4">
          <i class="ri-linkedin-fill"></i> linkedin.com/in/aslialimesimsek
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 border-t-2 pt-8">
      <p class="text-[10px] font-black tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-gray-500 mb-4">ABOUT THIS PORTFOLIO</p>
      <div class="max-w-2xl space-y-4 text-base leading-relaxed">
        <p>This site was built and deployed entirely by me. No dev team, no agency. It runs on an Astro framework, deployed via GitHub to Netlify, with content managed through code. I used Claude as a build partner throughout: for copy strategy, component logic, and iterating the case study structure in real time.</p>
        <p>It's a proof point. I don't just market technical products. I build with the tools I recommend. If you're hiring a PMM to lead your technical narrative, this is what hands-on looks like.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
